---
title: Thai Green Pork Meatball Soup with Daikon Noodles & Asian Greens
description: With a warm and aromatic soup, low-carb daikon noodles and succulent pork meatballs, it’s no wonder this divine
dish was a favourite at the testing table. It's bright, it's fun and most importantly, it tastes the part too - delicious!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-pork-meatball-soup-daikon-noodles-e86b6762.jpg
